  <brief_title>Predicting Cardiometabolic Risk in Mild-to-Moderate Obstructive Sleep Apnea: Inflammation vs. Apnea/Hypopnea Index</brief_title>
  <official_title>Predicting Cardiometabolic Risk in Mild-to-Moderate Obstructive Sleep Apnea: Inflammation vs. Apnea/Hypopnea Index</official_title>
